Option to rotate, flash, mode, filters, timer, exposure, effects, music, gallery for image clicked in story.

Option to apply a filter on the image clicked directly in the story.
Filters will not apply to images uploaded from mobile.
A Realtime filter applies while capturing an image in-camera from the story.
Filters effects similar to- 
Snapchat, 
Instagram, and
Tik Tok

Modules:
- Camera permission management
- Filter effect rendering
- Video recording
- High resolution photo taking
- Preparing of effects & resources with application launch